Dear <%= @subscription.user.full_name %>,

Thank you for subscribing to the <%= @article.blog.title %> blog. Each time a new blog is posted you will receive an email notification with the title of the new blog and a link directly to it. We hope that our blogs, composed by the writers of our curriculum, continue to assist with implementation and share useful information.

<% if @article.blog.global? %>
  <%= global_post_url(@article.slug, slug: @article.blog.slug) %>
<% else %>
  <%= curriculum_post_url(@article.slug, page_slug: @article.blog.page.slug, slug: @article.blog.slug) %>
<% end %>

